      "x": "OVERVIEW. Bonfil opens the whole cancer block with a precise definition and one emphasis he wanted to land early: a tumor is not made only of tumor cells. Get the definition and the two-compartment picture right and the rest of the lecture — benign vs malignant, nomenclature, carcinogens — has somewhere to attach."
